flowchart TD
    A([Start: ExplainabilityEngine]) --> B[Inputs<br/>schema_diff, type_changes, row_diff]

    %% ---------------- SEVERITY ----------------
    B --> C[Calculate Severity]
    C --> C1[Compute breakdown scores]

    C1 --> C2[Schema scoring<br/>removed, renamed, reordered]
    C1 --> C3[Type scoring<br/>int/float → string = high weight]
    C1 --> C4[Row scoring<br/>changes per 100 rows]

    C2 --> C5
    C3 --> C5
    C4 --> C5

    C5[Sum total score] --> C6[Map score to level<br/>Low / Medium / High / Critical]

    %% ---------------- EXPLANATIONS ----------------
    B --> D[Generate Explanations]

    D --> D1[Explain schema changes<br/>removed, added, renamed, reordered]
    D --> D2[Explain type changes<br/>risk-based messages]
    D --> D3[Explain row changes<br/>changed, missing, new rows]

    D1 --> D4
    D2 --> D4
    D3 --> D4

    D4{Any explanations?}
    D4 -- No --> D5[Add default: No significant changes]
    D4 -- Yes --> D6[Use collected explanations]

    %% ---------------- SUMMARY ----------------
    B --> E[Generate Change Summary]

    E --> E1[Schema stats<br/>added, removed, reordered, renamed]
    E --> E2[Type stats<br/>risk distribution]
    E --> E3[Row stats<br/>counts + percentage]

    %% ---------------- IMPACT ----------------
    C6 --> F[Explain Impact]
    E --> F

    F --> F1{Severity level}

    F1 -->|Low| F2[Minor impact<br/>likely safe]
    F1 -->|Medium| F3[Moderate impact<br/>review needed]
    F1 -->|High| F4[High impact<br/>risk to pipelines]
    F1 -->|Critical| F5[Critical impact<br/>immediate action]

    %% ---------------- OUTPUT ----------------
    C6 --> G
    D6 --> G
    D5 --> G
    E --> G
    F --> G

    G[Final Output<br/>severity, explanations,<br/>summary, impact] --> H([End])
